;Welcome back to the Naval Podcast where we post intermittently since 2020, I believe. We are going to talk about some &lt;strong&gt;How to Get Rich&lt;/strong&gt; content. I&amp;rsquo;ve pulled out some tweets from Naval&amp;rsquo;s Twitter from the last year. I got a little help from SuperGrok as well, and we&amp;rsquo;re just going to go through them.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
